text: Vasilios Lykomitros (born 15 June 1962) is a Greek rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Greek male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Greece Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
